the central DHIS2 database.

42
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:03,640
From her office in the city,
the regional health manager

43
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:07,020
can see, at a glance, how many
vaccines were administered

44
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:10,630
in each community and the
immunization rate for her region.

45
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:13,640
And at the Ministry of
Health, DHIS2 dashboards

46
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:16,840
measure the campaign's progress
