and desktop computers,

68
00:03:24,190 --> 00:03:27,790
and even submit limited data by SMS.

69
00:03:27,790 --> 00:03:31,520
Data submitted to DHIS2 is instantly saved

70
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:35,200
and can be accessible
from any connected device.

71
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:39,660
DHIS2 provides data collection
in even the most remote

72
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:41,920
and fragile settings where internet

73
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:44,083
and electricity may not be reliable.

74
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:48,300
Making important decisions
does not only depend

75
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:51,590
